[Bb]uilds/

# Unity user-specific settings
UserSettings/

# Generated Visual Studio / Rider solution and project files
*.csproj
*.unityproj
*.sln
*.suo
*.tmp
*.user
*.userprefs
*.pidb
*.booproj
*.svd
*.pdb
